title: doc: go1.7 release notes include typo for TLSConfig.NextProtos
body:
https://github.com/golang/go/blob/c6f19fe1ea5292f75618e3dcb2e2c4a9d1684aa6/doc/go1.7.html#L912

The release notes state the field as `TLSConfig.NextProto`, but it should in fact be `TLSConfig.NextProtos` (note the trailing `s`).
